&lt;h2 id=&quot;snapshot-tests&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;Snapshot tests&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This test vault enables snapshot testing of the garden compilation! To generate the snapshot:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;run &lt;code&gt;Generate Garden Snapshot&lt;/code&gt; from the command palette&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Snapshot generation is also run on plugin load.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
